                1,
                "Map Connector"
              ],
              "indent": 0,
              "code": 402
            },
            {
              "parameters": [
                "The Map Connector (also known as the Visual Editor) "
              ],
              "indent": 1,
              "code": 101
            },
            {
              "parameters": [
                "allows you to connect maps together."
              ],
              "indent": 1,
              "code": 401
            },
            {
              "parameters": [
                "In the Debug menu (F9 or in the pause menu), choose "
              ],
              "indent": 1,
              "code": 101
            },
            {
              "parameters": [
                "the \"Map Connections\" option."
              ],
              "indent": 1,
              "code": 401
            },
            {
              "parameters": [
                "Once there, choose a map to display by pressing the "
              ],
              "indent": 1,
              "code": 101
            },
            {
              "parameters": [
                "S key.  Select it and press the E key to edit its "
              ],
              "indent": 1,
              "code": 401
            },
            {
              "parameters": [
                "encounters, or double-click it to edit its metadata."
              ],
              "indent": 1,
              "code": 401
            },
            {
              "parameters": [
                "Add additional maps to the canvas by pressing the A "
              ],
              "indent": 1,
              "code": 101
            },
            {
              "parameters": [
                "key, and drag them around to connect them.  Maps "
              ],
              "indent": 1,
              "code": 401
            },
            {
              "parameters": [
